          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κατα - παύω</span></b> , fut. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">-σω</span>, aor. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κατέπαυσα</span>, subj. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">-παύσομεν</span>: <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">put an end to, quell;</span> of
