          anything (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἀγηνορίης, ἀφροσυνά̄ων</span>),
            <i><span class="en">Il. 22.457</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Od. 24.457</span></i>; ironically of killing, <i><span class="en">Il. 16.618</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
